twitter.pl
Copyright © 2010 - Jeremy Jack

A simple perl script that you can run from cron
to update your Twitter feed with your WoW achievements.

It requires Net::Twitter, XML::Feed, and Cache::FileCache

*/15 * * * * perl /root/wow/wow.pl

Twitter is pretty terrible.




